OL,3,CMan charged with murder of father
OL,4,Cstabbed in Yorkshire village
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a stabbing in a Yorkshire
OL,8,Fvillage over the weekend.
OL,10,F30-year-old Mason Jones was found with
OL,11,Fa stab wound at the junction of Main
OL,12,FStreet and Iron Row in Burley in
OL,13,FWharfedale Sunday morning.
OL,15,FHe later died of his injuries.
OL,17,FMason's family said they are still
OL,18,Ftrying to come to terms with their
OL,19,F"imaginable loss."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
